We design and build Wedding Website templates for engaged couples, and then host their website through our multi tenant web system.

## Template Theme

Timeless, "classic" theme.

## Template Requirements

These are required to make the website function properly and consistently with the rest of the themes.

**Absolutely no cards in the design. EVER.**

Must be mobile responsive (Using Container Queries)

Must have the following sections:

- Our Story
- Details
- Gallery
- RSVP
- FAQ
- Registry (Link out to) (No icons)
  - Crate and Barrel
  - Amazon
  - Williams Sonoma
  - Honeymoon Fund
